[This report states that the diagnosis of HFMD in the 2-year old child in
Kedah State was confirmed by a blood test. Information on the nature and
specificity of this test are important, since a first report from Singapore
suggests that both Enterovirus 71 and an undefined Coxsackie virus are
circulating in this epidemic. -Mod.CP
